{
  "notes": [
    "Single-user database: every table has `user_id` and it is always 1. You may omit `WHERE user_id = 1` — there is only one user.",
    "All timestamps are ISO 8601 strings stored in text columns (e.g. \"2026-03-18T14:30:00.000Z\"), UTC. Date-only fields (event_date, birth_date, date) are \"YYYY-MM-DD\". Compare/sort them as strings; use SQLite date()/strftime() for bucketing.",
    "Booleans are stored as integers 0/1 (e.g. is_filtered, starred, is_race, attended, notable, rewatch, is_home).",
    "is_filtered = 1 marks Last.fm rows the owner has hidden (junk scrobbles, misattributions). Analytical listening queries should filter `is_filtered = 0` unless you specifically want the raw data. lastfm_scrobbles has no is_filtered column — join through lastfm_tracks to filter.",
    "Rating scales differ by domain: watch_history.user_rating and movies.tmdb_rating / shows.tmdb_rating are 0-10 (real). discogs_collection.rating and discogs_wantlist.rating are 0-5 integers (0 = unrated). reading_items.rating is a small integer (may be null). There is no single global scale.",
    "Images: the shared `images` table keys on (domain, entity_type, entity_id). The public CDN URL is composed as https://cdn.dinakartumu.com/cdn-cgi/image/<transforms>/<r2_key>, and image_version is appended as a cache-busting query param (?v=<image_version>). Many domain tables also carry a denormalized image_key/poster_path for convenience. dominant_color/accent_color are hex strings; thumbhash is a compact placeholder blob.",
    "Cross-domain join keys: performers.lastfm_artist_id → lastfm_artists.id (concerts ↔ listening); collection_listening_xref links discogs_collection ↔ Last.fm play counts by matched name; trakt_collection.movie_id and watch_history.movie_id → movies.id (physical media ↔ watched films).",
    "Enums are stored as plain text. Notable ones: watch_history.source (plex|letterboxd|manual|trakt), trakt_collection.media_type (bluray|uhd_bluray|hddvd|dvd|digital), reading_items.status (unread|reading|finished), attended_events.category (sports|music|arts)."
  ],
  "tables": [
    {
      "name": "lastfm_artists",
      "purpose": "One row per artist scrobbled by the user, with playcount and enrichment (bio, genre, similar artists, Apple Music links).",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "name", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "mbid", "type": "text", "note": "MusicBrainz id, nullable" },
        {
          "name": "playcount",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "lifetime scrobble count"
        },
        {
          "name": "is_filtered",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "0/1; 1 = hidden from analytics"
        },
        {
          "name": "genre",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "primary genre (top allowlisted tag)"
        },
        {
          "name": "tags",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "JSON array of {name,count}"
        },
        { "name": "bio_summary", "type": "text" },
        {
          "name": "similar_artists",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "JSON array of similar artists the user also plays"
        },
        { "name": "apple_music_url", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "image_key", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "created_at", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "updated_at", "type": "text" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_albums",
      "purpose": "Albums scrobbled by the user.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "name", "type": "text" },
        {
          "name": "artist_id",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "→ lastfm_artists.id"
        },
        { "name": "playcount", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "is_filtered", "type": "integer", "note": "0/1" },
        {
          "name": "released_year",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "nullable, from Apple Music"
        },
        { "name": "total_tracks", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "apple_music_url", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "image_key", "type": "text" }
      ],
      "joins": ["artist_id → lastfm_artists.id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_tracks",
      "purpose": "Tracks scrobbled by the user (the grain that scrobbles reference).",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "name", "type": "text" },
        {
          "name": "artist_id",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "→ lastfm_artists.id"
        },
        {
          "name": "album_id",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "→ lastfm_albums.id, nullable"
        },
        { "name": "duration_ms", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "is_filtered", "type": "integer", "note": "0/1" },
        { "name": "apple_music_url", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "preview_url", "type": "text" }
      ],
      "joins": ["artist_id → lastfm_artists.id", "album_id → lastfm_albums.id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_scrobbles",
      "purpose": "Individual play events — one row per listen. The base fact table for listening.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "track_id", "type": "integer", "note": "→ lastfm_tracks.id" },
        {
          "name": "scrobbled_at",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "ISO 8601 timestamp of the play"
        }
      ],
      "joins": [
        "track_id → lastfm_tracks.id (then → lastfm_artists / lastfm_albums). Filter is_filtered via the track join."
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_top_artists",
      "purpose": "Precomputed top-artist rankings per Last.fm period (7day, 1month, 3month, 6month, 12month, overall).",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "period", "type": "text", "note": "Last.fm period key" },
        { "name": "rank", "type": "integer" },
        {
          "name": "artist_id",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "→ lastfm_artists.id"
        },
        {
          "name": "playcount",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "plays within the period"
        }
      ],
      "joins": ["artist_id → lastfm_artists.id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_top_albums",
      "purpose": "Precomputed top-album rankings per period.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "period", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "rank", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "album_id", "type": "integer", "note": "→ lastfm_albums.id" },
        { "name": "playcount", "type": "integer" }
      ],
      "joins": ["album_id → lastfm_albums.id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_top_tracks",
      "purpose": "Precomputed top-track rankings per period.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "period", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "rank", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "track_id", "type": "integer", "note": "→ lastfm_tracks.id" },
        { "name": "playcount", "type": "integer" }
      ],
      "joins": ["track_id → lastfm_tracks.id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_filters",
      "purpose": "User-defined filter rules that drive the is_filtered flags (which artists/tracks to hide).",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "filter_type", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "pattern", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "scope", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "reason", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_user_stats",
      "purpose": "Single-row lifetime listening totals (scrobbles, unique artists/albums/tracks).",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "total_scrobbles", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "unique_artists", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "unique_albums", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "unique_tracks", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "registered_date", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "updated_at", "type": "text" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_monthly_stats",
      "purpose": "Precomputed per-month listening totals (is_filtered=0 scope).",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "year_month", "type": "text", "note": "\"YYYY-MM\"" },
        { "name": "scrobbles", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "unique_artists", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "unique_albums", "type": "integer" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_yearly_stats",
      "purpose": "Precomputed per-year listening totals plus top artist of the year.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "year", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "scrobbles", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "unique_artists", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "unique_albums", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "unique_tracks", "type": "integer" },
        {
          "name": "top_artist_id",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "→ lastfm_artists.id, nullable"
        }
      ],
      "joins": ["top_artist_id → lastfm_artists.id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "lastfm_album_attribution_audit",
      "purpose": "Audit log for the one-time album-attribution repair migration. Rarely useful for user questions.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "original_album_id", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "original_album_name", "type": "text" },
        {
          "name": "action",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "KEEP_AS_VA | COLLAPSE_TO_PRIMARY | SPLIT_PER_ARTIST"
        },
        { "name": "tracks_moved", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "created_at", "type": "text" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "strava_activities",
      "purpose": "One row per Strava activity (mostly runs). Base fact table for running. Filter is_deleted = 0.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        {
          "name": "strava_id",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "upstream Strava activity id"
        },
        { "name": "name", "type": "text" },
        {
          "name": "sport_type",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "e.g. Run, TrailRun, Walk"
        },
        { "name": "distance_miles", "type": "real" },
        { "name": "distance_meters", "type": "real" },
        { "name": "moving_time_seconds", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "total_elevation_gain_feet", "type": "real" },
        { "name": "start_date", "type": "text", "note": "ISO 8601, UTC" },
        {
          "name": "start_date_local",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "ISO 8601, venue-local"
        },
        { "name": "city", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "state", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "pace_min_per_mile", "type": "real", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "pace_formatted", "type": "text", "note": "e.g. \"8:32\"" },
        { "name": "average_heartrate", "type": "real", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "calories", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "is_race", "type": "integer", "note": "0/1" },
        { "name": "is_deleted", "type": "integer", "note": "0/1; filter = 0" },
        {
          "name": "gear_id",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "→ strava_gear.strava_gear_id, nullable"
        },
        { "name": "strava_url", "type": "text" }
      ],
      "joins": [
        "gear_id → strava_gear.strava_gear_id",
        "strava_id → strava_splits.activity_strava_id"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "strava_splits",
      "purpose": "Per-mile splits for an activity.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        {
          "name": "activity_strava_id",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "→ strava_activities.strava_id"
        },
        { "name": "split_number", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "distance_miles", "type": "real" },
        { "name": "moving_time_seconds", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "pace_formatted", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "average_heartrate", "type": "real", "note": "nullable" }
      ],
      "joins": ["activity_strava_id → strava_activities.strava_id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "strava_gear",
      "purpose": "Shoes / gear with accumulated mileage.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        {
          "name": "strava_gear_id",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "upstream id, matches strava_activities.gear_id"
        },
        { "name": "name", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "brand", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "model", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "distance_miles", "type": "real" },
        { "name": "is_retired", "type": "integer", "note": "0/1" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "strava_personal_records",
      "purpose": "Best times per distance (e.g. fastest 5K).",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        {
          "name": "distance",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "machine key, e.g. \"5k\""
        },
        { "name": "distance_label", "type": "text", "note": "display label" },
        { "name": "time_seconds", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "time_formatted", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "pace_formatted", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "date", "type": "text", "note": "YYYY-MM-DD" },
        {
          "name": "activity_strava_id",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "→ strava_activities.strava_id"
        },
        { "name": "activity_name", "type": "text" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "strava_year_summaries",
      "purpose": "Precomputed per-year running totals.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "year", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "total_runs", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "total_distance_miles", "type": "real" },
        { "name": "total_elevation_feet", "type": "real" },
        { "name": "total_duration_seconds", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "avg_pace_formatted", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "longest_run_miles", "type": "real" },
        { "name": "race_count", "type": "integer" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "strava_lifetime_stats",
      "purpose": "Single-row lifetime running totals, streaks, and Eddington number.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "total_runs", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "total_distance_miles", "type": "real" },
        { "name": "total_elevation_feet", "type": "real" },
        { "name": "total_duration_seconds", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "avg_pace_formatted", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "years_active", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "first_run", "type": "text", "note": "ISO 8601, nullable" },
        { "name": "eddington_number", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "current_streak_days", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "longest_streak_days", "type": "integer" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "movies",
      "purpose": "One row per unique film. watch_history references this; a movie can be watched many times.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "title", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "year", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "tmdb_id", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable, unique" },
        { "name": "imdb_id", "type": "text", "note": "nullable, unique" },
        { "name": "runtime", "type": "integer", "note": "minutes, nullable" },
        { "name": "tmdb_rating", "type": "real", "note": "0-10, nullable" },
        { "name": "summary", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "content_rating", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        {
          "name": "poster_path",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "TMDB path, nullable"
        },
        { "name": "image_key", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" }
      ],
      "joins": [
        "id ← watch_history.movie_id",
        "id ← movie_genres.movie_id ← genres",
        "id ← movie_directors.movie_id ← directors",
        "id ← trakt_collection.movie_id"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "genres",
      "purpose": "Movie genre lookup (shared name → id).",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "name", "type": "text", "note": "unique" }
      ],
      "joins": ["id ← movie_genres.genre_id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "movie_genres",
      "purpose": "Many-to-many join between movies and genres.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "movie_id", "type": "integer", "note": "→ movies.id" },
        { "name": "genre_id", "type": "integer", "note": "→ genres.id" }
      ],
      "joins": ["movie_id → movies.id", "genre_id → genres.id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "directors",
      "purpose": "Director lookup (shared name → id).",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "name", "type": "text", "note": "unique" }
      ],
      "joins": ["id ← movie_directors.director_id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "movie_directors",
      "purpose": "Many-to-many join between movies and directors.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "movie_id", "type": "integer", "note": "→ movies.id" },
        { "name": "director_id", "type": "integer", "note": "→ directors.id" }
      ],
      "joins": ["movie_id → movies.id", "director_id → directors.id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "watch_history",
      "purpose": "One row per movie viewing event (rewatches produce multiple rows). Base fact table for watching films.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "movie_id", "type": "integer", "note": "→ movies.id" },
        { "name": "watched_at", "type": "text", "note": "ISO 8601" },
        {
          "name": "source",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "plex | letterboxd | manual | trakt"
        },
        { "name": "user_rating", "type": "real", "note": "0-10, nullable" },
        { "name": "rewatch", "type": "integer", "note": "0/1" },
        { "name": "review", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        {
          "name": "review_url",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "nullable Letterboxd review link"
        },
        { "name": "percent_complete", "type": "real", "note": "nullable" }
      ],
      "joins": ["movie_id → movies.id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "watch_stats",
      "purpose": "Single-row denormalized watching totals (movies, shows, episodes, watch time).",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "total_movies", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "total_watch_time_s", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "movies_this_year", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "total_shows", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "total_episodes_watched", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "episodes_this_year", "type": "integer" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "shows",
      "purpose": "One row per TV show. episodes_watched references this.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "title", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "year", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "tmdb_id", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "trakt_id", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "tmdb_rating", "type": "real", "note": "0-10, nullable" },
        { "name": "total_seasons", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "total_episodes", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "poster_path", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "image_key", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" }
      ],
      "joins": ["id ← episodes_watched.show_id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "episodes_watched",
      "purpose": "One row per episode viewing event.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        { "name": "show_id", "type": "integer", "note": "→ shows.id" },
        { "name": "season_number", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "episode_number", "type": "integer" },
        { "name": "title", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "watched_at", "type": "text", "note": "ISO 8601" },
        { "name": "source", "type": "text", "note": "plex | trakt" }
      ],
      "joins": ["show_id → shows.id"]
    },
    {
      "name": "discogs_releases",
      "purpose": "Catalog metadata for a Discogs release (album pressing). discogs_collection references these.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
        {
          "name": "discogs_id",
          "type": "integer",
          "note": "upstream release id"
        },
        { "name": "title", "type": "text" },
        { "name": "year", "type": "integer", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "genres", "type": "text", "note": "JSON array" },
        { "name": "styles", "type": "text", "note": "JSON array" },
        {
          "name": "formats",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "JSON array (e.g. Vinyl, CD)"
        },
        {
          "name": "labels",
          "type": "text",
          "note": "JSON array of {name,catno}"
        },
        { "name": "country", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        { "name": "cover_url", "type": "text", "note": "nullable" },
        {
          "name": "lowest_price",
          "type": "real",
          "note": "nullable, market price"
        }
      ],
      "joins": [
        "id ← discogs_collection.release_id",
        "id ← discogs_release_artists.release_id ← discogs_artists"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "discogs_artists",
      "purpose": "Artist metadata for releases in the collection.",
      "columns": [
        { "name": "id", "type": "integer", "note": "PK" },
